Sentencas: Ba1-xCo0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-delta oxides (x = 0, 0.05 and 0.10) were optimized as potential cathodes on oxygen ionic conductor electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Composition and microstructure Optimization and operation stability of barium deficient Ba1-xCo0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ perovskite oxide electrodes

Sentencas: The creation of additional oxygen vacancies in Ba0.9Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-delta was confirmed.
Titulo: Composition and microstructure Optimization and operation stability of barium deficient Ba1-xCo0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ perovskite oxide electrodes

Sentencas: Low polarization resistances of 0.015, 0.029 and 0.089 Omega cm(2) were achieved at 700, 650 and 600 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Composition and microstructure Optimization and operation stability of barium deficient Ba1-xCo0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ perovskite oxide electrodes

Sentencas: By further optimizing the microstructure of the Ba0.9Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-delta electrode by using polyvinyl butyral as a pore former and adjusting the sintering temperature, the maximum power density was improved from 682 to 955 mW cm(-2) at 650 degrees C.
Titulo: Composition and microstructure Optimization and operation stability of barium deficient Ba1-xCo0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ perovskite oxide electrodes

Sentencas: The operational stability of the Ba0.9Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-delta electrode was also investigated.
Titulo: Composition and microstructure Optimization and operation stability of barium deficient Ba1-xCo0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ perovskite oxide electrodes

Sentencas: The CO2 in the surrounding air was detrimental to the oxygen reduction reaction; however, the performance of the cell was recovered after removing the CO2 in the air at 650 or 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Composition and microstructure Optimization and operation stability of barium deficient Ba1-xCo0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ perovskite oxide electrodes

Sentencas: In addition, the Ba0.9Co0.2Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-delta electrode in symmetrical cells exhibited a stable performance at 650 degrees C for 400 h and maintained a reliable performance after repeated thermal cycles from room temperature to 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Composition and microstructure Optimization and operation stability of barium deficient Ba1-xCo0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ perovskite oxide electrodes

Sentencas: The results showed that Ba0.9Co0.3Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-delta was a promising cathode material for practical application in IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Composition and microstructure Optimization and operation stability of barium deficient Ba1-xCo0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ perovskite oxide electrodes
